name: Houschka Rounded_85% (iOS14-16)
author: Evelyn (ev_ynw)
description:
85% size. Install 'Houschka Rounded' for normal character size.

Only compatible on iOS14-16. Separate packages for iOS13 are available.

Installed to: /Library/Themes/[fontname].theme/

Apply with theming engines e.g. SnowBoard. Package name = Fonts.

Need help? Link to tutorials in my pinned tweet
